title: A Daystar Is Born
itunes:title: A Daystar Is Born
description:
WED 8/24 - His Toronto fam calls him Daystar Peterson but the hit artist known as Tory Lanez joins The Breakfast Club! We talk to him about his album "I Told You" (in stores now), why he & Drake throw shade at each other, how his sound is influenced by fellow artists & more!
